06:12.539 --> 06:14.542
Yeah, we also have lights.

06:15.675 --> 06:16.875
The Southland continues

06:16.877 --> 06:18.810
to experience a
widespread outbreak,

06:20.882 --> 06:22.184
And no more coffee.

06:23.151 --> 06:24.286
That's great.

06:26.187 --> 06:27.452
Guy, where's my good knife?

06:27.454 --> 06:29.123
