Ah.

37:23.509 --> 37:24.574
Guy?

37:24.576 --> 37:26.109
Oh, hey.

37:26.111 --> 37:27.710
I heard loud noises.

37:27.712 --> 37:29.381
Yeah, it was
probably just, uh,

37:30.515 --> 37:32.549
probably just stuff
falling off of stuff.

37:32.551 --> 37:33.716
Yeah, we're okay.

37:33.718 --> 37:34.650
The fence is tight.

37:34.652 --> 37:35.654
